      "content": "hey i think something is actually wrong. i just saw the exact same guy walking his dog in downtown chicago and then five minutes later i saw him again in a completely different neighborhood near the lake. it wasn't just a lookalike, it was the same jacket, same dog, everything. it felt like the world just... repeated. do u think this could be a resource limit in the simulation or something?",
