    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not pareidolia though. i know what i saw. it felt less like a coincidence and more like a hiccup in the rendering. a glitch. even the lighting felt slightly off right when it happened, like the textures hadn't fully loaded. if this is just \"coincidence\" then how do you explain the feeling that the logic of the world just stalled for a second? don't you think it's possible that the system is struggling to keep up with the processing load?",
